title: Catalyst Black is a new shooter game from the makers of Vainglory
content:
Vainglory is one of the memorable games that truly stood out back in the day. It’s a Multiplayer Online Battle Arena (MOBA) developed by Super Evil Mega Corp (SEMC). Vainglory easily deserved a seat on the best iPad games list. However, its servers were taken down back in 2020. Now it remains as a Community

The post Catalyst Black is a new shooter game from the makers of Vainglory appeared first on XDA.
description: Catalyst Black is a new shooter game developed by Super Evil Mega Corp, the makers of Vainglory. It launches worlwide next month.
